message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with signal processing and analysis of music signals. cs.AI is also likely as the paper uses statistical methods and machine learning techniques. cs.LG is another possible category as the paper uses Markov random fields. cs.SI is also possible as the paper deals with information retrieval from music signals. cs.IR is another possible category as the paper deals with transcription of music signals.
